#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
string s;
map<string,int> Mp;
int days[] = {0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
int getint(string &s){
    int ret = 0;
    for (int i=0; i<s.length(); i++){
        int t = s[i] - '0';
        ret = ret*10 + t;
    }
    return ret;
}
int main(){
    int T; cin>>T;
    Mp["JAN"] = 1; Mp["FEB"] = 2; Mp["MAR"] = 3; Mp["APR"] = 4; Mp["MAY"] = 5; Mp["JUN"]=6;
    Mp["JUL"] = 7; Mp["AUG"] = 8; Mp["SEP"] = 9; Mp["OCT"] = 10;  Mp["NOV"] = 11; Mp["DEC"] = 12;

    for (int i=1; i<=T; i++){
        cin>>s;
        int d,m,y;
        string day = s.substr(0,2);
        string month = s.substr(3,3);
        string year = s.substr(7,4);
        y = getint(year);
        d = getint(day);
        m = Mp[month];
        int cnt = 0;
        bool leap = false;
        if ((y%400==0)or(y%4==0 and y%100!=0)){leap = true;}
        for (int i=1; i<m; i++){
            int cur = days[i];
            if (i==2){
                if (leap){cur++;}
            }
            cnt+=cur;
        }
        cnt+=d;

        cout<<"Case "<<i<<": ";
        if (cnt<=300){
            cout<<cnt<<" Hundreds\n";
        }
        else if ((cnt>300)and(cnt<=360)){
            cout<<cnt-300<<" Tens\n";
        }
        else if (cnt>360){
            cout<<cnt-360<<" Ones\n";
        }
    }
}
